data.name: label19.Text
data.value:
Before using the DownCraft SPRX V4, make sure to install the EBOOT + MC.sprx into your console and load Minecraft. Don't forget to change your PS3 language to: English United States. You need to use Minecraft BLES01976 Press the button "Connect To SPRX V4" once you are in a world with the SPRX installed, when you start Minecraft it should send you a welcome message if you got this notification, everything is working correctly.
Press L1 + DPAD UP to open the menu Press DPAD UP / DOWN to navigate through the menu Press X to select a options / page Press O to close a page
